foundry-python-gamedev-extras (1.0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Drop python3-opencv to foundry-cv (atelier-only); removes
    libopencv-viz → libvtk9.5 (~275 MiB) from anvil and sprite.
  * Add libonnxruntime-dev — ONNX model inference engine (~20 MiB),
    pairs with OpenCV DNN for game-dev AI pipelines.

